{
  "texts": [
    "Based on its exhaustive nature, this research stands as one of the most holistic inquiries to date into the performance of LLMs in the NER domain.",
    "Furthermore, it carves a niche by exploring the impact of fine-tuning on LLMs for NER tasks, distinguishing our efforts from other existing research and reinforcing the study's unique contribution to the field.",
    "While our study offers valuable insights, it is not without its limitations.",
    "The dataset utilized in this research is relatively constrained, comprising only 91 VAERS reports.",
    "This limited scope might impede the generalizability of our findings to broader contexts."
  ]
}